{"tid":1692967,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學車一問","createTime":"2019-11-04T10:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T02:50:19.000Z","uid":1202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"022116ffa4d7f139e287258e71cad533eb922574","tid":1692967,"uid":1202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"考棍Van<br />\n想問下，開車停車前其實係咪要睇曬兩邊鏡？因為師傅冇提過，唔知係咪必須？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6342ae97446c70f582b41f53ea145ce6b517c6","tid":1692967,"uid":41995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022116ffa4d7f139e287258e71cad533eb922574","tid":1692967,"uid":1202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"考棍Van<br />\n想問下，開車停車前其實係咪要睇曬兩邊鏡？因為師傅冇提過，唔知係咪必須？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"係，左右兩面鏡都要望，最好望埋中鏡"},{"pid":"dede8b9a86eb5c32c810dfbe26d1895f0db8ab8d","tid":1692967,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"唔係必須<br />\n但你次次都唔睇可能會當輕微錯誤<br />\n如果咁啱有人有車係度照開車就會嚴重錯誤"},{"pid":"55cd773a94c7bd52e352c533fa1f6093f0afa1b0","tid":1692967,"uid":335233,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"啊包皮哥 如果你唔望開車 旁邊一架大貨車撞你<br />\n<br />\n都還好，但如果你車到攝出黎既人咁點？"},{"pid":"3a68d4b2a4e729154569815af9e9fee16b6b22a8","tid":1692967,"uid":51115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:05:30.000Z","msg":"如果有電單車係你開車嗰下攝過來 你冇望鏡就真係恭喜你 其實你考到車都要望"},{"pid":"422b8efc4275aa00d04ef63b54b403d5a686051d","tid":1692967,"uid":141704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:08:13.000Z","msg":"停車開車 望中鏡兩邊鏡<br />\n有行人係路邊想過都收慢/收停架車<br />\n有電單車插上黎記得收慢 啤實佢<br />\nCut線望鏡望盲點 過完車再望番佢<br />\n應快則快 應慢則慢<br />\n考完記得熄匙入一波<br />\n利申幾日前pass"},{"pid":"4bf20463eadd8c3b4d4361266bf1178dca0814f4","tid":1692967,"uid":319129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:10:48.000Z","msg":"開車前 左右中鏡都要望 要好撚大動作！"},{"pid":"684e29fc097054dc93cb1d9f14982790e5622ac8","tid":1692967,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"睇左少幾個剔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787a4603c5f41671ee093cd6187b9068479bb723","tid":1692967,"uid":181774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"開車前(其實加速都係)望左右鏡,提防街車左右兩邊攝入嚟<br />\n學車試過後面DC9照過雙白線係右邊爬頭,所以唔好老馮以為雙白線就無車cut入嚟<br />\n停車時(其實減速都係)望後鏡,提防後車跟得太貼剎唔切"},{"pid":"03016ba3de7e837ade92c5166347523146d2ace1","tid":1692967,"uid":1202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"收到曬！多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccf4e8579a08ffb7db0d0d5cc75736428e7cb55","tid":1692967,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運"},{"pid":"d1ba9685515746558bbf5c26421f9d5a343f0647","tid":1692967,"uid":89801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:50:19.000Z","msg":"師傅唔提 唔識問師傅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}